title: 800. Breaking Down Trade Value Charts & Last 5 First-Round Picks for All 32 Teams
itunes:title: 800. Breaking Down Trade Value Charts & Last 5 First-Round Picks for All 32 Teams
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys look at the trade value charts for the big trades this offseason including Deshaun Watson, Russell Wilson, Davante Adams and Tyreek Hill. Then for the rest of the show, the duo break down the last 5 first-round picks for all 32 teams.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
